ing: 1 (10.75 ounce) can  Campbell'sÂ® Condensed Cream of Chicken Soup (Regular or 98% Fat Free)
des: "This creamy crowd-pleasing side dish features summer squash, carrot, stuffing mix and cheese baked in a creamy sauce. Crispy on top and creamy in the center, this favorite side dish is a winner on any menu."
ins:
Mix stuffing and butter. Reserve 1/2 cup stuffing mixture and spoon remaining into a 2 quart shallow baking dish.
Mix soup, sour cream, yellow squash, zucchini, carrot and cheese. Spread over stuffing mixture and sprinkle with reserved stuffing mixture.
Bake at 350 degrees F for 40 minutes or until hot.
